<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>306</hymn_number>
<title>AA DAWHMI THLA CAMNAK DUM CH306</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh a kan hngahnak dum cu a um, Aa dawh ngaingai mi hmun cu a um,
 Bawipa a um ca zeizong te a ceu, Aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum a si.

[C1]
   Maw aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum, thlacamnak dum, Maw aa dawh bikmi
   thlacamnak dum, Khamhtu a kan hngah ko, Kutka cu a hun cang, Khi aa
   dawhmi thlacamnak dum ah.

[V2]
 Jesuh a kan hngahnak dum cu a um, Thilrit he kan luhnak dum a si,
 Bawipa hmurka in hnemhnak bia ka theih, Aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum chungah.

[C2]
   Maw aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum, thlacamnak dum, Maw aa dawh bikmi
   thlacamnak dum, Khamhtu a kan hngah ko, Kutka cu a hun cang, Khi aa
   dawhmi thlacamnak dum ah.

[V3]
 Jesuh a kan hngahnak dum cu a um, Amah ton awkah nang zong an auh, A
 hmai ah kun in thluachuahnak co tuah, Aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum chungah.

[C3]
   Maw aa dawhmi thlacamnak dum, thlacamnak dum, Maw aa dawh bikmi
   thlacamnak dum, Khamhtu a kan hngah ko, Kutka cu a hun cang, Khi aa
   dawhmi thlacamnak dum ah.</lyrics>
</song>